        "meta_description": "The restaurant Ristorante Da Giovanni is a family-owned establishment that has been highly praised by Michelin. The staff are very kind and make you feel at home, while the view of Isola Bella is stunning. The food here is as authentic as it gets for a very reasonable price, and the portions are huge. Try the mussels cooked in garlic or the spaghetti with clams.",
