        "text": "SuSunday: 7:00 PM–10:45 PM\n\nMoMonday: 7:00 PM–10:30 PM\n\nTuTuesday: 7:00 PM–10:45 PM\n\nWeWednesday: 7:00 PM–10:45 PM\n\nThThursday: 7:00 PM–10:45 PM\n\nFrFriday: 7:00 PM–10:45 PM\n\nSaSaturday: 7:00 PM–10:45 PM\n\nIn Toarmina I stayed for four evenings and my principle is to enjoy a variety of dishes in different restaurants and cafes. But this time I changed my principles and ate only in this restaurant because it did not disappoint and the dishes made me enjoy the whole menu. the food and atmosphere were fantastic! Thanks to the Giovanni family and the waiters! Also, the pistachio cake was delicious!"
